    "description": "<strong>MonoRaceVR</strong> is a monobike racing in Virtual Reality. The unique control of the monobike is as close to reality as possible: acceleration, braking and turns due to the tilt of the body. It can't be played without a headset, as the control system is VR-only.<br><br>In the Demo, we want to offer to experience new sensations and leave feedback in the comments.<br><br><strong>Our next steps:</strong><br>- New racing tracks and bikes<br>- Online Muliplayer<br>- Career mode<br>- Mini-games<br>- Achievements, Stats, Leaderboards<br>- And even more interesting content",
